reviewText: It was sent back because of not able to play on my dvd
I had not forgotten about this gem from the past. What fun to watch! buy these if you enjoy good old TV!

Season 6 contines with many fine stories and a new score by Marty Paich.  Ed Brown, Mark Sanger and Fran Belding are back.  Mark Sanger graduates from law school in this year's show and must make decisions about his future in "Down Two Roads."
All in all a fine year.
I am really enjoying watching these old shows. The packaging is a little tight. I had to tare open the box to get the dvd's out. The picture quality is very good. All in all I would recomend.
Im a huge fan of Raymond Burr as you can tell. Matter a fact I ordered 2 bottles of his wine.

IRONSIDE VIA "PAL" VIA AUSTRALIA....ONLY WAY TO GET IT ... BECAUSE ONLY 1ST FOUR SEASONS WERE RELEASED IN USA....THANKS "DOWN UNDER" ...NOW IRONSIDE "ROLLS ON" ...GREAT SET WITH GREAT QUALITY AND SOUND...IF YOU ARE A RAYMOND BURR FAN GET IT...MIGHT COST A BIT MORE BUT IT IS WELL WORTH IT...
Excellent. Well written. Good writers and well acted out. Would never buy a product if they remade the series with another actor.
